description: Price Adjustment & Increased Rent roll for September 1st 2025.  This turnkey 3 family asset is perfect for a 1031 exchange buyer or savvy investor looking for a high grossing income with low maintenance costs. This asset has 13 Bedrooms and 6 bathrooms in total. Located on the East side of South Boston just steps away from restaurants, shops, public transportation and the beach. Renovations units include stainless steel appliances in modern kitchens, brand new bathrooms , hardwood floors throughout, Central AC & Heat, rubber roof. Outdoor space including a deck and large yard.  This property will be a great investment for any owner looking to enter into the South Boston market.
